{"id":9623,"date":"2020-10-09T03:10:09","date_gmt":"2020-10-09T03:10:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=9623"},"modified":"2021-05-11T09:46:00","modified_gmt":"2021-05-11T09:46:00","slug":"xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that\/","title":{"rendered":"8 XU H\u01af\u1edaNG THI\u1ebeT K\u1ebe N\u1ed8I TH\u1ea4T PH\u1ed4 BI\u1ebeN N\u0102M 2020"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t nh\u00e0 \u1edf thay \u0111\u1ed5i theo t\u1eebng n\u0103m t\u1eeb c\u00e1ch ph\u1ed1i m\u00e0u, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u. \u0110\u00e3 n\u1eeda n\u0103m 2020 tr\u00f4i qua, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn, t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0u c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2020 &#8211; Classic Blue t\u1edbi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u trong kh\u00f4ng gian s\u00f4ng,&#8230; C\u00f9ng Byzan Interior c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt 8 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong n\u0103m nay.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Trang tr\u00ed tr\u1ea7n nh\u00e0&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tr\u1ea7n nh\u00e0 thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng nguy\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea1ch cao, n\u0103m 2020 c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng trang tr\u00ed b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u mang tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, tr\u1ea7n nh\u00e0 \u1ed1p g\u01b0\u01a1ng alu v\u1eeba khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o v\u1eeba gi\u00fap t\u0103ng chi\u1ec1u cao cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, n\u1ebfu gia ch\u1ee7 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch s\u1ef1 \u1ea5m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ed1p g\u1ed7 cho tr\u1ea7n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap kh\u00f4ng gian n\u00e0y tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng kh\u00e1c. Ng\u00e0y nay, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n gi\u00fap vi\u1ec7c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m g\u1ed7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eaft \u1edf d\u1ea1ng mi\u1ebfng th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eaft th\u00e0nh t\u1eebng nan g\u1ed7 ho\u1eb7c t\u1ea1o ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-6-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that\" class=\"wp-image-9624\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-6-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-6-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-6-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-6.jpg 1125w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><figcaption><em>Tr\u1ea7n nh\u00e0 \u1ed1p g\u01b0\u01a1ng alu n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>\u00c1p d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0u c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2020 &#8211; Classic Blue (Xanh c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n)<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Theo Pantone, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a n\u0103m nay ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Classic Blue &#8211; Xanh lam c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n. \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc y\u00ean b\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin; \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi n\u00f3 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i con ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi nhau. M\u00e0u xu h\u01b0\u1edbng do Pantone c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 m\u1ed7i n\u0103m c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ee9c mua c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2020.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"564\" height=\"563\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that-1.jpg\" alt=\"xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that\" class=\"wp-image-9626\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that-1.jpg 564w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that-1-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 564px) 100vw, 564px\" \/><figcaption><em>Xanh lam c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n &#8211; Classic Blue <\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, Classic Blue \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng. N\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t di\u1ec7n t\u00edch l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 s\u01a1n t\u01b0\u1eddng, ho\u1eb7c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n nh\u1ecf, sofa, r\u00e8m,&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"563\" height=\"650\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that.jpg\" alt=\"xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that\" class=\"wp-image-9625\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that.jpg 563w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-cont