rong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1eadt li\u1ec7u t\u1eeb t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong n\u0103m 2020 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ebf t\u1edbi nh\u01b0 g\u1ed7 d\u00e1n, \u0111\u1ea5t nung, m\u00e2y tre \u0111an,&#8230; Nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u d\u00e2n d\u00e3 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u d\u00e2n d\u00e3 n\u00e0y trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t nh\u00e0 \u1edf gi\u00fap ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 t\u0103ng th\u00eam c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u1ea5m c\u00fang, t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. Nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 gh\u1ebf, k\u1ec7, \u0111\u00e8n, th\u1ea3m, gi\u1ecf treo, ch\u1eadu hoa,&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/1-6-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai\" class=\"wp-image-9628\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/1-6-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/1-6-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/1-6-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/1-6-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/1-6.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption><em>\u0110\u00e8n tr\u1ea7n b\u00e0n \u0103n l\u00e0m t\u1eeb tre m\u1ed9c m\u1ea1c<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i h\u1ecdc m\u1ea1ch, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong trong kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft g\u1eb7p trong nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a n\u0103m nay. Chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho gh\u1ebf sofa, gh\u1ebf \u0103n, chi ti\u1ebft trang tr\u00ed,&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong trang tr\u00ed nh\u00e0 \u1edf, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong u\u1ed1n l\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc b\u00e0n tr\u00e0 h\u00ecnh tr\u1ecdng, sofa c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n t\u1ef1a l\u01b0ng bo tr\u00f2n, \u0111\u00e8n ch\u00f9m, g\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh oval,&#8230; \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o v\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng gian h\u00e0i h\u00f2a.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-7-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that\" class=\"wp-image-9629\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-7-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-7-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-7-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-7-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-7-450x253.jpg 450w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-7-140x79.jpg 140w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-7.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption><em>B\u00e0n tr\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>\u0110\u00e1 c\u1ea9m th\u1ea1ch&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u00e1 c\u1ea9m th\u1ea1ch ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb trong c\u00e1c xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2020, b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 tinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd l\u1ed7i m\u1ed1t. D\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u trong kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, mang t\u1edbi c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c sang tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. \u0110\u00e1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u1ecb \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u1edbn quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 \u1ed1p m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng, \u1ed1p m\u1eb7t b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea3o, s\u00e0n nh\u00e0, s\u1ea3nh ch\u00ednh,&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-8-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai\" class=\"wp-image-9630\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-8-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-8-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-8-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-8-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-8-450x253.jpg 450w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-8-140x79.jpg 140w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/2-8.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption><em>Ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ea9m th\u1ea1ch \u1ed1p t\u01b0\u1eddng tivi<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u nhung<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mang h\u01a1i h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 1970, ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u nhung m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t trong n\u0103m 2020. Trong su\u1ed1t n\u1eeda n\u0103m 2020, ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u nhung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u \u00e1i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong nhi\u1ec1u v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea3 trong phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i l\u1eabn sang tr\u1ecdng, \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o trong m\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u nhung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng trong c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 g\u1ed1i, gh\u1ebf b\u00e0nh, gh\u1ebf ottoman,&#8230; v\u00e0 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 l\u1ee5a, da ho\u1eb7c satin \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng rung c\u1ea3m kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"564\" height=\"563\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that-2.jpg\" alt=\"thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai\" class=\"wp-image-9631\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that-2.jpg 564w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that-2-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that-2-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 564px) 100vw, 564px\" \/><figcaption><em>B\u1ed9 sofa nhung \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>V\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u1ee9ng&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e2y xanh tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng khu v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u1ee9ng, nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y c\u00e2y xanh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u gia \u0111\u00ecnh \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian c\u00e2y xanh gi\u00fap ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 th\u00eam t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u00e1t v\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean g\u1ea7n g\u0169i h\u01a1n v\u1edbi thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean. C\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t, v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u1ee9ng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y c\u00e2y xanh, hoa c\u1ecf l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch th\u00f4ng minh \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ho\u1eb7c che \u0111i m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn m\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"819\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/vuon-dung-819x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9632\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/vuon-dung-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/vuon-dung-240x300.jpg 240w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/vuon-dung-768x960.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/vuon-dung.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 819px) 100vw, 819px\" \/><figcaption><em>V\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i c\u00e2y xanh<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Byzan Interior (m\u1edf trong tab m\u1edbi)\" href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/\" target=\"_blank\">Byzan Interior<\/a> \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb 8 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2020. Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng b\u1ed5 \u00edch cho qu\u00fd b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;<strong>&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"10+ m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i sang tr\u1ecdng (m\u1edf trong tab m\u1edbi)\" href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/10-mau-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-sang-trong\/\" target=\"_blank\">10+ m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i sang tr\u1ecdng<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/phong-cach-noi-that-dan-dau-xu-huong-nam-2020\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u0103m 2020 (m\u1edf trong tab m\u1edbi)\">Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u0103m 2020<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t nh\u00e0 \u1edf thay \u0111\u1ed5i theo t\u1eebng n\u0103m t\u1eeb c\u00e1ch ph\u1ed1i m\u00e0u, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u. \u0110\u00e3 n\u1eeda n\u0103m 2020 tr\u00f4i qua, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn, t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0u c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2020 &#8211; Classic Blue t\u1edbi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":10466,"comment_stat